premise_source_doc_sentence: Her tenth album , Shakira  (  2014  )  , is preceded by its lead single , `` Ca n't Remember to Forget You '' .
Colombian singer and songwriter Shakira has released four video albums and appeared in fifty-one music videos , seven films , and four documentaries .

Colombian singer and songwriter Shakira has released eleven studio albums , four live albums , two compilation albums , forty-nine singles  (  including nine as featured artist  )  , and nine promotional singles .
